      • draw

        void draw(android.graphics.Canvas canvas,
          android.graphics.Paint paint,
          float x,
          float y,
          DataPointInterface dataPoint)
        called when drawing a single data point. use the x and y coordinates to draw your drawing at this point.
        Parameters:
        canvas - canvas to draw on
        paint - internal paint object. this has the correct color. But you can use your own paint.
        x - x-coordinate the point has to be drawn to
        y - y-coordinate the point has to be drawn to
        dataPoint - the related data point
